General.Name: Newcourt Acquisition Corp Unit
General.Description: Newcourt Acquisition Corp does not have significant operations. It intends to effect a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. Newcourt Acquisition Corp was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Oakland, California. Newcourt Acquisition Corp operates as a subsidiary of Newcourt SPAC Sponsor LLC.
